  "textPreview": "Free June 9 event: How to win brand visibility when AI decides what gets seen →\nSolutions\nTools\nResources\nPricing\nEN\nSign in\nRequest a demo\nStart free trial\nWebsite Competitor Analysis Tool\n\nRun a complete website competitor analysis and see how your rivals perform in SEO, PPC, and AI search. Find their traffic sources, top content, and strategy gaps\n\nRun your first check now. No sign-up or credit card required. Free for 14 days.\n\nUnited States\nAnalyze\n\nTrusted by 40,000+ agencies\n\nMaster Generative Engine Optimization by tracking competitor visibility in AI search\n\nGo beyond monitoring. Use AI search competitive analysis tools to detect prompts and keywords that surface rivals in AI answers and replace their mentions with yours\n\nCompetitive analysis for AI search engines\n\nAnalyze how your competitors show up in AI Overviews, AI Mode, ChatGPT, Perplexity, and Gemini\n\nMeasure how visible any competitor is across AI answers\n\nIdentify when AI search engines mention or cite specific rivals\n\nInspect prompts and AI answers that trigger competitor mentions\n\nBenchmark multiple competitors to see their AI visibility gaps\n\nMonitor changes over time to spot trends and new opportunities\n\nStart free trial\nGet an overview of competitor site visits in one click\n\nReview rival paid and organic campaigns to see their dynamics\n\nMonthly clicks estimated with AI\n\nTop-performing competitor keywords and pages\n\nCompetitors' traffic cost\n\nStart free trial\nThe biggest Database in the US\nAmericas\n428M\nUSA\n144M\nCanada\n46M\nEurope\n1.1B\nGermany\n64M\nUnited Kingdom\n106M\nAsia\n453M\nUAE\n18M\nJapan\n21M\nStart free trial\nBring competitor data into your own tools and workflows\n\nPull competitor traffic, keyword, and AI visibility data directly via API or access it live inside Claude, ChatGPT, or any AI assistant via MCP\n\nCompetitor data without the manual pull\n\nAccess traffic estimates, keyword gaps, backlink data, and AI search visibility metrics for any domain directly via SE Ranking API.\n\nCompetitive rep",
